summary: LOS ANGELES, Feb. 19, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Angel City Football Club (ACFC) today announced CarMax (NYSE: KMX), the nation’s largest retailer of used cars, as a Founding Partner and its Official Used Auto Retailer.
